reviewText: any kid from the 90s can remember growing up with these shows knows they are amazing for kids to watch growing up especially on a halloween weekend.

These are all older animated shows that are no longer on the regular TV or the cable we have.  My kids love all of them.  They love Rolie Polie the most and Seven Little Monsters.  I like Franklin the best.  Maggis and the Ferocious Beast is all of our lease favorites.
